  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and
      pharmacodynamics of the investigational drug ACU-4429 in subjects with geographic atrophy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
